  Locus:
    Page: 100
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Desire
---
Attachment is real death. Non-attachment is eternal life. Attachment brings
manifold miseries. Non-attachment brings manifold bliss. Attachment
contracts the heart. Non-attachment expands the heart ad infinitum.
